---
source: tests/cli.rs
expression: help
---
List recent activity

Usage: list [OPTIONS]

Options:
      --user <USERNAME>
          Exact personal-profile username whose visible activity should be listed

      --limit <N>
          Server request page size (maximum 50)

          [default: 10]

      --before-id <TOKEN>
          Fetch activity before this endpoint-native token

  -h, --help
          Print help
